node.text:
Paw pads are naturally tough, but they should not be overly dry. When skin is dry, it’s more prone to injury from splitting and developing deep & painful cracks. Healthy, conditioned paws are flexible and actually allow for dogs to get a better grip! I recommend healing paws with 100% natural Paw Soother. It’s pet-safe and works super fast to get paws healthy again.
